These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: salsa, country, ambient, folk, rock
There are 5 different nationalities: brazilian, british, chinese, pakistani, russian
5 different pets are kept: frog, hamster, horse, rabbit, snake
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, cain, siglo, chaman, bongani
 1. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 2. the bongani-smoker is the fan of rock##1
 3. the cain-smoker is on the right of the brazilian##1
 4. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the chinese##1
 5. the owner of the hamster is the pakistani##1
 6. the british is the fan of country##1
 7. the owner of the frog is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
 8. the british is on the far left##1
 9. the fan of salsa is on the right of the british##1
10. the fan of folk is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
11. the owner of the hamster is the bluemaster-smoker##1
12. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| Music-Genre         | country  | salsa    | folk | ambient    | rock  |
| Nationality   | british  | brazilian | chinese | pakistani | russian  |
| Pet           | frog     | snake     | rabbit  | hamster   | horse    |
| Cigar         | siglo | chaman    | cain | bluemaster  | bongani |

