.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
There 5 different types of food: artichoke, cucumber, kiwi, lettuce, watermelon
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: dahlia, daffodil, balloon-flower, marigold, zinnia
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, documentary, family, martial-arts
5 different games are played: scrabble, snooker, domino, go, bridge
 1. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 2. the person playing domino is the person watching animation movies##1
 3. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing go##1
 4. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
 6. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 7. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 8. the person eating kiwi is the person watching documentary movies##1
 9. the person playing go is the person eating kiwi##1
10. the person eating cucumber is in the middle##1
11. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person playing domino##1
12. the person eating kiwi is the person who growsdaffodil##1
13. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Food          | kiwi        | watermelon | cucumber     | lettuce      | artichoke  |
| Flower           | daffodil   | balloon-flower | zinnia    | marigold | dahlia |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | family     | martial-arts | adventure    | animation  |
| Game   | go     | snooker | scrabble    | bridge      | domino    |

