.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-3::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, milk, sprite, tea, water
The people have 5 different jobs:  musician, writer, accountant, security-guard, mechanic
5 different pets are kept: frog, guinea-pig, dog, cat, chinchilla
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike, scooter, snowmobile, train
 1. the security-guard is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 2. the musician is on the right of the accountant##1
 3. the owner of the frog is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
 5. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1
 6. the writer is on the far left##1
 7. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 8. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 9. the person driving the train is in the middle##1
10. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
11. the owner of the dog is the musician##1
12. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
13. the person drinking tea is the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | tea          | sprite  | milk       | fanta     | water      |
| Job         | writer | mechanic | security-guard  | accountant   | musician    |
| Pet   | guinea-pig        | chinchilla | frog | cat    | dog   |
| Transport     | helicopter   | scooter | train      | quad-bike | snowmobile |

