.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-4::.
There 5 different types of food: kale, lemon, papaya, plum, zucchini
There are 5 different favourite beverages: juice, soy-milk, milk, fanta, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: country, gospel, indie, pop, techno
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, chaman, tiparillo, prince, davidoff
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the fan of country##1
 2. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 3. the fan of gospel is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 4. the fan of country is the person drinking juice##1
 5. the person drinking milk is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 6. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 7. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 8. the davidoff-smoker is in the middle##1
 9. the fan of pop is on the left of the person eating kale##1
10. the person eating zucchini is the fan of indie##1
11. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
12. the cain-smoker is on the left of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Food          | plum        | kale       | papaya | lemon   | zucchini  |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | milk | soy-milk | juice   | fanta |
| Music-Genre   | pop         | techno     | gospel | country | indie     |
| Cigar     | cain        | chaman        | davidoff    | prince    | tiparillo      |

