 1. the owner of the horse is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 2. the person who's sport is sailing is the person traveling to nizza##1
 3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 4. the person eating potato is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 6. the person traveling to london is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 7. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
 8. the owner of the guinea-pig is in the middle##1
 9. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
10. the person eating potato is on the far right##1
11. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
12. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |      4       |      5      |
