 3. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
 4. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the game-smoker##1
 5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 6. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 7. the person watching scientific movies is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 8. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person drinking water##1
 9. the aristoff-smoker is on the far left##1
10. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
11. the fonseca-smoker is in the middle##1
12. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the blend-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
