 3. the person playing scrabble is on the far left##1
 4. the german is on the right of the nigerian##1
 5. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far right##1
 8. the person playing chess is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 9. the german is the person playing monopoly##1
10. the turkish is in the middle##1
11. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the turkish##1
12. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
13. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
14. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |       4       |    5     |
