.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-17::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, iced-tea, juice, milk
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: crime, martial-arts, romance, scientific, western
There are 5 different favourite colors: fuchsia, aquamarine, mauve, amber, blood-red
The people have 5 different jobs:  musician, librarian, mechanic, social-worker, project-manager
 1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
 2. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
 3. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
 4. the librarian is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
 5. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the project-manager##1
 6. the mechanic is on the right of the librarian##1
 7. the person watching martial-arts movies is the musician##1
 8. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 9. the project-manager is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
10. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
11. the social-worker is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
12. the person watching romance movies is the person who likes amber##1
13. the person watching western movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Beverage      | 7up      | cola       | milk         | juice  | iced-tea |
| Movie-Genre   | romance  | scientific | martial-arts | crime  | western  |
| Color   | amber    | aquamarine    | fuchsia        | blood-red | mauve     |
| Job           | librarian | mechanic      | musician       | social-worker   | project-manager   |

