.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-18::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: zinnia, rose, begonia, bellflower, orchid
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, country, folk, gospel, jazz
There are 5 different nationalities: italian, british, pakistani, spanish, nigerian
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, rowing, sailing, swimming, volleyball
 1. the spanish is on the right of the nigerian##1
 2. the fan of folk is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 3. the pakistani is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 4. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 5. the nigerian is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 6. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
 7. the person who growsrose is the person who's sport is basketball##1
 8. the person who growsbegonia is the fan of country##1
 9. the british is in the middle##1
10. the italian is the fan of jazz##1
11. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
12. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the spanish##1
13. the person who growsbellflower is the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |     5     |
| Flower   | rose      | bellflower | begonia  | orchid    | zinnia |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | jazz     | country | blues      | folk      |
| Nationality           | pakistani       | italian     | british     | nigerian     | spanish   |
| Sport         | basketball | swimming | rowing  | volleyball | sailing   |

