.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-19::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, lemonade, milk, tea
The people have 5 different hobbies: fishing, dancing, board-games, skydiving, singing
5 different pets are kept: bird, fish, goat, rabbit, turtle
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: october, september, november, june, july
 1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 3. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in september is the person drinking lemonade##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in october is in the middle##1
10. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
11. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
12. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person drinking tea##1
13. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4    |   5    |
| Beverage      | lemonade | tea    | cola   | milk   | coffee |
| Hobby   | fishing    | board-games   | singing | skydiving | dancing  |
| Pet           | fish     | rabbit | goat   | turtle | bird   |
| Birthday     | september  | july   | october    | june   | november |

