.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-20::.
5 different pets are kept: dog, lizard, hedgehog, goat, horse
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, country, pop, punk, salsa
The people have 5 different hobbies: writing, sudoku, skydiving, rock-climbing, puzzles
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, scooter, snowmobile, train, tram
 1. the owner of the hedgehog is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of punk is the person driving the helicopter##1
 3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 4. the fan of blues is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 5. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
 6. the person driving the train is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 7. the fan of pop is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 8. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 9. the person driving the tram is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
10. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1
11. the fan of blues is on the far right##1
12. the fan of salsa is in the middle##1
13. the person who's hobby is writing is the owner of the goat##1
14. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3    |     4      |   5    |
| Pet      | lizard | goat   | hedgehog    | dog       | horse |
| Music-Genre   | pop           | country   | salsa   | punk       | blues  |
| Hobby   | sudoku       | writing | skydiving | rock-climbing     | puzzles   |
| Transport     | snowmobile    | scooter   | train   | helicopter | tram   |

 